data.description: Welcome to Falcon Bridge! Convenience, Convenience, Convenience with no city tax!!! Offering a short drive to both Air Station Cherry Point and Downtown New Bern, this home is exactly what you have been searching for! This FOUR bedroom, three bathroom, + BONUS room, offers ample space and plenty of storage. The owners suite boasts two walk-in closets, a dual vanity, a standing shower and a separate soaking tub. Enjoy an open concept living room, kitchen, and dining area. The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, stainless steel kitchen appliances and gorgeous white cabinets. Don't miss the two additional bedrooms on the first floor that share a full bathroom. The upstairs houses the 4th bedroom, another large full bathroom, AND a BONUS room! This home is a must see. Schedule your showing today!Seller is offering $2,000 Use As You Choose!
